2️⃣ Deployment Strategy (Step-wise)
Step 1: Server Setup

Install Linux (Ubuntu Server)

Install Java / Python runtime (based on implementation)

Install MySQL / PostgreSQL

Install Apache/Nginx for frontend

Step 2: Database Configuration

Create database for:

Logs

Users

Incident Reports

Configure DB credentials securely

Step 3: Backend Deployment

Deploy backend application (Spring Boot / Flask / Node.js)
Step 4: Frontend Deployment

Deploy UI files (HTML/CSS/React)

Connect frontend to backend APIs

Step 5: API Communication Setup

Use RESTful APIs (HTTP/HTTPS)

JSON format for data exchange

Configure CORS policies

Expose REST APIs

Configure API endpoints for:

Upload Logs

Analyze Logs

Generate Alerts

Trigger Response
